headline: Parker to Webcast Annual Meeting of Shareholders on October 22, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. Eastern
summary: CLEVELAND, Oct. 14, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Parker Hannifin Corporation (NYSE: PH), the global leader in motion and control technologies, today announced that it will webcast its Annual Meeting of Shareholders, which is scheduled for Wednesday, October 22, 2025, at 9:00 a.m., Eastern time. The webcast will be accessible on Parker's investor website at investors.parker.com and will be archived on the site for one year.
